This is easily my favorite place in Vegas, especially to go with a group of friends.
It's a must do.
Giant tables filled with happy people singing, dancing on tables, pounding beers by the liter.
The host is fun and does a great job getting the crowd riled up with stein-holding and liter-pounding competitions.
