I guess I don't like German food so much even though I am Polish?
Maybe it is because they invaded us in the big one: WWII.
I should add service during dinner was as equally good (or better considering the circumstances) as was during lunch although we did not have any special food requests.
I would still recommend this place not so much for the food, but, because of the live music and the paddle spanking for fun.
By the way I recommend the dark draft Dunkel, which was pretty tasty.

