We started out with a pretzel and giant beers, well the pretzel was giant too now that I think about it...anyway, both were dee-lish.
I particularly liked the cheese spread and brown honey mustard dipping sauces that came with the pretzel.
I'm normally a fan of schnitzel, but I thought I'd try something different this time.
