Beer was flowing, shots were plentiful and a few in our group got spanked...literally...numerous times.
Don't be a snob like I was - just because something's a little touristy doesn't mean it can't be a good time.
I go to Vegas for work A LOT - I'd happily go to Hofbrau again if for no other reason than to forget about work for a minute.
