Unfortunately the cute waitresses and ambiance has gone by the wayside.
The DJ on my Saturday Night(I'm still sitting at the table) hosted 2 ridiculous contests which were preceded by 30 minute idiotic monologues...The band barely played, and the spankings were the only highlight.
The guy on the mic should go back to OG's to call Destiny to the stage...

Make sure you get Apple Schnapps and get a spanking to go  with it!
